---
title: Herbed Chicken with Feta & Orange Salad Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: This salad comes together at lightning speed without skimping on sophistication. You’ll sear herb-seasoned chicken and serve on a bed of mixed greens, crumbled feta, sweet-tart cara cara orange slices, and a crisp one-two punch of croutons and nutty pecans all tossed in tangy honey-Dijon dressing. Pair with a side of buttery garlic-herb bread for a fast, easy, complete meal that never fails to please.
